2 Property Visualizations

plotStressStrain <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10){
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x = dataset$GrainMeanEVM[[step]], y = dataset$GrainMeanSVM[[step]])) +
        xlim(0, 0.06) +
        ylim(0, 1200) + 
        ggtitle(paste('Stress Strain Curve - ',deparse(substitute(dataset)) ,' Step ', step, sep='')) +
        xlab('Grain Mean EVM') +
        ylab('Grain Mean SVM'))
  }
}

plotSVMDistr <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10, ylimit = 0.03){
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot(alpha = 0.2) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMinSVM[[step]], color = 'Min')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMinSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Min'), bins = 50) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianSVM[[step]], color = 'Median')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMedianSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Median'), bins = 50) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxSVM[[step]], color = 'Max')) +
            geom_histogram(alpha = 0.2, aes(x = dataset$GrainMaxSVM[[step]], y = ..density.., color = 'Max'), bins = 50) +
            xlim(0, signif(max(dataset$GrainMaxSVM), 2)) + 
            ylim(0, ylimit) + 
            ggtitle(paste('SVM Distribution - ', deparse(substitute(dataset)), sep='')) +
            xlab('Grain SVM (MPa)') + 
            ylab('Density') + 
            guides(color = guide_legend(title = 'Property'))
            )
  }
}

plotSlipSystems <- function(dataset, maxSteps = 10) {
  for (step in 1:maxSteps){
    print(ggplot() + 
            geom_histogram(aes(x = dataset$SlipSystems[[step]], y=..density..), bins = 40, alpha = 0.4) +
            geom_density(aes(x = dataset$SlipSystems[[step]])) +
            xlim(0, 10) +
            ylim(0, 1) +
            ggtitle('Slip System Distribution')
    )
  }
}
